ßgeblich daran beteiligt? Welches Bild des Epochenjahres 1989 wurde dabei entworfen? Sebastian Klinge geht diesen Fragen nach und zeichnet zugleich ein aktuelles Porträt der Geschichtspolitik im 21. Jahrhundert.  aThe historical policy regarding the GDR is as young as it is controversial. This volume follows up on its particular logic via the example of the »Remembrance Year 2009«: Which image of the landmark year 1989 was painted 20 years after the fall of the Berlin Wall?  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aCollective memoryzGermanyxHistoryy21st century. 4a1989. 4aDDR. 4aDeutsche Geschichte. 4aErinnerungskultur. 4aGeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aGeschichtswissenschaft. 4aMauerfall. 4aPolitik. 4aZeitgeschichte. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh  a1989.  aContemporary History.  aEast Germany.  aGerman History.  aHistory of the 20th Century.  aMemory Culture.  aPolitics.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2015z9783110438635oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070099208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2014z9783110401226oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839427415zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839427415423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839427415/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-070099-2  PP P